
Upgrade from version 2.0 to any newer version
---------------------------------------------

* Read the Release Notes relevent to the new version if any.
* Run install/upgrade.php. It will detect if there are some database upgrades to do.

Upgrade from older version (version < 2.0)
------------------------------------------

* Read the Release Notes relevent to the new version if any.
* Check the install/upgrade_to_xxx directories and follow the upgrade procedures.

